title: Westwood 2 bed / 2 bath w/ 2 balconies, fireplace, parking
neighborhood: Westwood 90024, UCLA, Brentwood, West LA, Beverly Hills
posting_body: ['Westwood 2 bedroom apartment with 2 baths near UCLA!', 'This apartment features central air, gas fireplace, 2 balconies and more!', 'Kitchen is equipped with granite countertops, and appliances including a gas stove, an oven, a dishwasher, and a refrigerator.', 'Our gated access community offers features such as a soothing spa, fitness center, disability access, a picnic area with barbecue, and onsite maintenance.', 'Walking distance to everything in Westwood Village, just one block south of Wilshire and one block west of Westwood Boulevard.', 'Underground parking included and extra storage available.', 'Rent is $3,595 per month with a 12-month lease term.', 'For appointment or for questions, call us today at', 'show contact info', '.', 'For more property photos and to view our floor plans, or for further details visit:  <URL>', '1441 Midvale Avenue', 'Westwood, Los Angeles, California, 90024', 'Brentwood, West LA, Beverly Hills', 'This 2 bedroom apartment offers the following features:', 'Granite Countertops', 'Dishwasher', 'Central Air', 'Extra Storage', '2 Balconies', 'Gas Stove & Oven', 'Dishwasher', 'Refrigerator', 'The building amenities include the following features:', 'Spa Access', 'Fitness Center', 'Access to Public Transportation', 'Assigned Parking', 'Garage', 'Elevator', 'Beautiful Landscaping', 'Cable Available', 'Covered Parking', 'Disclaimer: Pictures are a representation but may not be of the exact apartment.', 'Advertised unit availability, rental rates, and terms are updated every 24 hours and conditions are subject to change without notice.', 'Please call for latest availability details.']
